Package: directoryr
Type: Package
Title: Build Sub-Directories in Shiny Server to Host Apps in Packages
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jon", "Hill", email = "jon.mark.hill@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")))
Maintainer: Jonathan Hill <jon.mark.hill@gmail.com>
Description: This is a continuous integration utility package for Shiny Server.
    If a package is installed on the server, this package can be used to maintain
    Shiny Server sub-directories with a yaml file and fully automate shiny app
    deployments.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
